    </decisions>
    <description>Customers leave us an NPS score, and for Premium Target customers who leave us a low NPS score - we create a case for the Billing Upsell Owners to act upon.
04/06/2023 - Updated flow to only create cases if a large segment account has a Low or Promotor NPS or if a small or medium segment account has a Low NPS. Did a clean up on the label of some of the nodes. (Sprint 5 - 2023)
03/28/24 - PE - Update case ownership to be assigned to SaaS Owner set on the account level
04/18/24 - JC - Udpate to remove Case Creation on NPS Scores &lt;9-10</description>
    <environments>Default</environments>
    <formulas>
        <description>Sets the case subject based on the formula to incorporate different NPS scores</description>
        <name>CaseSubject</name>
        <dataType>String</dataType>
        <expression>IF ({!$Record.Wootric__Score__c} &lt; 9, &apos;Low NPS&apos;, &apos;Promotor NPS&apos;)</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>for_IsChanged</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>OR( (ISCHANGED({!$Record.Wootric__Score__c})) , ( ISCHANGED({!$Record.Wootric__Survey_Feedback__c}) ) )</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>for_IsNew</name>
        <dataType>Boolean</dataType>
        <expression>IsNew()</expression>
    </formulas>
    <formulas>
        <name>for_Last90days</name>
        <dataType>Date</dataType>
        <expression>{!$Flow.CurrentDate}-90</expression>
    </formulas>
    <interviewLabel>Resource: Low NPS Checks {!$Flow.CurrentDateTime}</interviewLabel>
    <label>Resource: Low NPS Checks</label>
